<item>
            <title>[FELIX-1660] karaf should not hardcode the &quot;system&quot; location of its maven-like repository</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1660</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A lot of stuff in the karaf setup is configurable, but the directory in which the maven-like bundle repo is located is not.  For geronimo integration we&apos;d like to not surprise our users and use &quot;repository&quot; instead of &quot;system&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m attaching a minimal patch to enable configuring this, I&apos;ll refine it if the idea meets with approval.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
